title: KDE Frameworks 5.112 Improves Support for NetworkManager 1.44, Fixes Bugs
description:
KDE Frameworks 5.112 open-source software suite is out now with improved support for NetworkManager 1.44, as well as various bug and crash fixes.

title: OBS Studio 30 Released with Support for Intel QSV H264, HEVC, and AV1 on Linux
description:
OBS Studio 30 open-source screencasting and streaming app is now available for download with Intel QSV H264, HEVC, and AV1 support on Linux, as well as numerous other changes and new features.
